---
title: BBQ Dry-Rub Chicken Thighs with Corn and Ranch Dressing
description: Summer is perfect for a family BBQ! Enjoy BBQ-rubbed chicken, corn and golden roasted potatoes! You'll never want butter on corn again after you try it slathered in ranch dressing!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/hauts-de-cuisse-de-poulet-aux-epices-bbq-f1738160.jpg
